Exercise:

Create an EC2 instance in Ohio Region with below details:
1) Create a VPC with your name
2) Create a subnet as private-yourname under above VPC
3) Create a keypair with yourname-21sep
4) Create a Server under above VPC/Subnet and with above keypair
5) Use variable for AMI and it must ask for AMI ID during the runtime
6) Hardware should be defaulted to t2.micro but should be changeable by providing value as "t2.nano" under terraform.tfvars file
7) Server name it should ask during the runtime